--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.1.1 (2020-11-27)
E: Improve Monit configuration file

* Version 2.1.0 (2020-11-23)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (opensmtpd_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 2.0.2 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 2.0.1 (2020-05-06)
B: Correct default aliases and secret path

* Version 2.0.0 (2020-05-06)
C: Add support for OpenSMTPD 6.6
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.0.1 (2019-01-31)
B: Ensure service is started before running command 'smtpctl aliases'

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.4.3 (2018-12-06)
E: Improve Ansible role overall
E: Change default value of 'opensmtpd_listen_all' parameter

* Version 0.4.2 (2018-12-04)
E: Add 'no_log' parameter to sensitive tasks

* Version 0.4.1 (2018-12-04)
B: Remove single quotes from 'secrets' file

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-12-01)
F: Add support for managing 'secrets'

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-01-10)
E: Improve Jinja2 filters

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-05)
F: Initial release
